definition: to pay/to hand over to/classifier for pairs or sets of things

sentences.english: Cash accounting means that the income is only recognised when the money comes in.
sentences.chinese: 現金實付制會計意味着只有收到現金時才確認收入。

sentences.english: Regarding the actual out-of-pocket cost, this varies from situation to situation.
sentences.chinese: 至於實際出實付成本，這情況各不相同的情況。
